 2014-03492014-03-31,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  ,  DESD
ActFinancial Administration Act
SubjectGovernment of Canada Website
PrecisOrder authorizing the Minister of Employment and Social Development to provide additional services as well as any activity related to (1) administer the social media accounts of the departments listed in schedule I, I.1 or II of the Financial Administration Act; (2) publish the mobile applications of those departments on third party mobile application stores and on the Government of Canada website; and (3) provide online citizen engagement tools for use by those departments.
